  "Two protons are initially very far apart and are pushed together until they are separated by 1 × 10⁻¹⁵ m (about the size of a nucleus). How much electric potential energy is stored? (k = 9 × 10⁹ N·m²/C², e = 1.6 × 10⁻¹⁹ C)": "",
